&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;아동학대의 대표적인 유형은 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;가지로 신체학대&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;정서학대&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;성학대&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;방임 및 유기가 있는데요&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;유형별로 아동학대를 당하는 아이들의 특징에 대해 알아보도록 하겠습니다&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
